---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const serviceTitle = 'Social Media Autopilot';
const metadata = {
  title: `${serviceTitle} - Capybara Studios`,
  description: `Put your social media on autopilot and maintain a consistent, engaging online presence with less effort.`,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <header class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter font-heading dark:text-gray-200">
          {serviceTitle}
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-muted dark:text-slate-300">
          Automate your social media content creation, scheduling, and cross-platform publishing. Stay visible and
          consistent with less effort.
        </p>
      </header>

      <article class="prose dark:prose-invert lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            The Challenge: The Never-Ending Social Media Treadmill
          </h2>
          <p>
            Is managing multiple social media platforms, creating engaging content, and posting consistently feeling
            like a full-time job? Many businesses struggle to maintain an active and effective social media presence due
            to the time and effort required. Common hurdles include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Lack of time to create fresh content regularly.</li>
            <li>Inconsistent posting schedules leading to audience disengagement.</li>
            <li>
              Difficulty managing and repurposing content across different platforms (e.g., LinkedIn, X, Facebook,
              Instagram).
            </li>
            <li>Struggling to keep up with trends and create timely, relevant posts.</li>
            <li>Spending too much manual effort on scheduling and publishing.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            The Capybara Studios Way: Smart Social Media Automation
          </h2>
          <p>
            Our Social Media Autopilot service helps you streamline your social media management, save time, and
            maintain a consistent brand voice across platforms. We leverage automation to handle the heavy lifting, so
            you can focus on strategy and engagement. Our solution includes:
          </p>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3">
            <li>
              <strong>Content Curation & AI-Assisted Creation:</strong> We can help set up systems to curate relevant industry
              content or use AI tools to assist in drafting social media posts, captions, and ideas based on your brand and
              topics.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Automated Content Repurposing:</strong> Turn blog posts into a series of tweets, key presentation slides
              into Instagram carousels, or video snippets into engaging shortsâ€”automatically.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Smart Scheduling & Evergreen Queues:</strong> We configure tools to schedule your posts at optimal
              times for each platform and build evergreen content queues to ensure your profiles are always active, even
              when you're busy.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Cross-Platform Publishing:</strong> Publish or schedule content to multiple social media platforms
              (e.g., LinkedIn, X/Twitter, Facebook Pages/Groups, Instagram, Pinterest) from a single dashboard or automated
              workflow.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Basic Performance Dashboards:</strong> We can help set up ways to track key metrics like engagement,
              reach, and follower growth to understand what's working.
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="mt-4">
            With Social Media Autopilot, you can build a stronger online presence, engage your audience more
            effectively, and free up valuable time to focus on other core aspects of your business.
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center py-8 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            Ready to Make Social Media Effortless?
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-6 text-muted dark:text-slate-300">
            Let's automate your social media strategy so you can connect with your audience consistently.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-3">Activate Your Autopilot</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

